                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                        </head>
                        <p>Loy W. Henderson, on October 4, addressed the Wellesley Club in
                            Washington, D.C., on “American Aid to Greece—A Step toward Lasting
                            Peace”; for the text of his address, see Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, October 19, 1947, page 772.</p>
